high_descs: Turn left and approach the white table against the wall.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn around and cross the room to the sink.
Slice the potato that's in the sink.
Move to the left a few inches.
Put the knife in the sink to the left of the potato and egg.
Move back to the right a few inches.
Pick up a slice of the potato.
Turn around and move to the stove in the corner on the right.
Put the potato slice in the frying pan on the back left burner.
Pick up the frying pan with the potato slice.
Turn around and move to the white table that's sitting against the wall.
With the handle pointing towards the chair, set the frying pan on the table between the knife and the soap bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a frying pan holding a potato slice on the table.

high_descs: turn left and walk over to the small square kitchen table
grab a butter knife off of the kitchen table
turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink ahead
slice up the brown vegetable inside of the sink
move to the left of the sink a bit
place the knife inside of the sink
move to the right side of the sink a bit
grab a slice of the vegetable out of the sink
turn around and walk over to the stove on the right side corner of the room
place the vegetable slice in the pan on the back left burner
pick up the pan off of the burner
turn around and walk over to the small square table on the right
set the pan down on the table
anns.task_desc: set a pan with a vegetable slice in it on the kitchen table

high_descs: Walk forward past the fridge, then turn left and face the white table along the wall next to the chair.
Pick up the knife that is in the middle of the table.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Slice half of the potato that is in the sink.
Move slightly to the left, still facing the sink.
Put the knife in the sink on the left hand side of the partially sliced potato.
Move slightly to the right, still facing the sink.
Take one slice of potato from out of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the stove top in the corner of the kitchen, to the right of the white table and chair.
Put the potato slice into the metal skillet on the back left burner of the stove top.
Pick up the metal skillet from the back left burner.
Turn around and walk to the table and chair near the stove top.  Stand facing the white table with the stove top on your right hand side and the chair on the left of the table.
Put the metal skillet with the potato slice onto the middle of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a metal skillet with a potato slice onto a white table.

high_descs: Go straight, turn left, and go to the white table with the spatula on it.
Take the silver knife from the table.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Slice the potato in the sink.
Turn left, go to the counter next to the sink, and turn right.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn right, go to the sink, and turn left.
Take a slice of potato from the sink.
Turn around, go to the wall, turn right, and go to the oven.
Put the potato in the square pan on top of the oven.
Take the square pan from the oven.
Turn around and go to the white table with the spatula.
Put the square pan on the white table next to the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a slice of potato on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the small white table.
Take the knife on the table.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Slice the potato in the sink.
Turn left, then right and approach the left side of the link.
Put the knife in the sink.
Go back to the right side of the sink.
Take a potato slice from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the stove on the right.
Put the slice in the pan on the back burner.
Take the pan from the stove.
Turn around and walk to the small white table on the right.
Put the pan on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a potato slice on the small white table.

high_descs: Move to the left, turn around, and face the small white table.
Pick the knife up from off of the white table.
Turn around to face the sink.
Slice the potato in the sink.
Move slightly to the left of the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Move slightly to the right of the sink.
Pick up a slice of the potato.
Turn around and move to the right to face the stove.
Place the potato in the pan on the stove.
Pick up the pan with the potato in it.
Turn around and go to the right to face the white table.
Place the pan on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Place the pan with the potato in it on the white table.
